{"title":"解放汤阴","authors":["林湘辑"],"dates":[{"year":1947,"month":7,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放汤阴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"林湘辑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汤阴近日斗争大恶霸苏伯寅时，平民会主席刘代和一群小伙子，你一句我一句编成了一个快板，如下："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八路军，真能干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大军来打汤阴县，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"声声要捉孙老殿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孙老殿，发了愁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"先掀平房后掀楼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掀了楼，还不算，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六关的房子烧个遍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老百姓没法站，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"逼得城里去逃难。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"×　　×　　×"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲戚也来找，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朋友也来叫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孙老殿说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“命令如山倒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁敢瞎胡闹，”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把咱大家送到岳王庙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"×　　×　　×"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃罢饭，没事干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来了苏伯寅忘八蛋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个见了害了怕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那个见了打战战。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苏伯寅说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“叫你大家去挖沟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"至死也得往前干。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"×　　×　　×"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们军队打开汤阴县，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"街公所，关里按，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘同志、李同志爱护咱："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往年的伤心事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都来诉一番。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说起了苏伯寅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"罪恶大如天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"救富不救贫（注），"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两国当汉奸（指日、美），"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四大条件他都犯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三次大会斗争他，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说的伯寅没啥辩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"区公所，支撑咱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"先分家业，后分地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪毙苏伯寅住了戏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（注）苏伯寅曾任国民党救济委员，专以粮款“救济”脱亡地主。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}